D = interp(B,C,3/9);

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw(A--D);

label("$A$", A, N);
label("$B$", B, SW);
label("$C$", C, SE);
label("$D$", D, S);
[/asy]

Then
\[\cos \angle BAD = \cos \frac{A}{2} = \sqrt{\frac{1 + \cos A}{2}} = \boxed{\frac{\sqrt{34}}{12}}.\]

